#x27;Fraunces:Medium&#x27;,sans-serif] leading-[1.4] relative shrink-0 text-[#0d0d0d] text-[32px] w-full">Better Sourcing for Businesses</p><p class="font-[&#x27;Rubik:Regular&#x27;,sans-serif] leading-[28px] relative shrink-0 text-[#1e4a35] text-[18px] w-full">Hotels, caterers, processors, and global buyers access quality produce and ingredients with full transparency and consistent supply. </p></div></div><div class="content-stretch flex gap-[32px] items-start justify-center overflow-clip relative shrink-0 w-full" data-name="Tab Horizontal"><div class="flex h-0 items-center justify-center relative self-center shrink-0 w-0" style="container-type:size;--transform-inner-width:1185;--transform-inner-height:21"><div class="flex-none rotate-90 w-[100cqh]"><div class="h-0 relative w-full" data-name="Border"><svg class="absolute block inset-0 size-full" fill="none" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><line id="Border" opacity="0" stroke="var(--stroke-0, black)" stroke-width="2" x2="201" y1="-1" y2="-1"></line></svg></div></div></div><div class="content-stretch flex flex-[1_0_0] flex-col gap-[16px] items-start justify-center min-w-px not-italic overflow-clip relative" data-name="Content"><p class="font-[&#x27;Fraunces:Medium&#x27;,sans-serif] leading-[1.4] relative shrink-0 text-[#0d0d0d] text-[32px] w-full">Better Food Systems for Everyone</p><p class="font-[&#x27;Rubik:Regular&#x27;,sans-serif] leading-[28px] relative shrink-0 text-[#1e4a35] text-[18px] w-full">By efficiently matching supply and demand, we ensure more food is consumed rather than wasted. Food systems will shape our planet&#x27;s future, with Africa leading the way. At Farm to Feed, we create the infrastructure for a more inclusive, resilient, and waste-free future.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute flex h-[555.649px] items-center justify-center left-[699.82px] top-[61.68px] w-[574.366px]" style="--transform-inner-width:1185;--transform-inner-height:21"><div class="flex-none rotate-[9.8